Package cz.cvut.fel.omo.smartfarm.builder

Class FarmBuilder

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.omo.smartfarm.builder.FarmBuilder
public class FarmBuilder extends Object
FarmBuilder is a utility class for constructing a Farm instance. It provides a fluent API for adding various elements such as fields, farmers, buildings, equipment, animals, and products to a farm configuration.
